{"tid":1369733,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"勇武派對唔住，今次又係和理非主場","createTime":"2019-07-26T18:42:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-26T23:06:59.000Z","uid":222614,"like":27,"dislike":106,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"26b4494c6793f63497c3f066c8ece9115c2c8b3b","tid":1369733,"uid":222614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T18:42:11.000Z","msg":"由於可以肯定中共會派人入村破壞<br />\n<br />\n大家一但入村，所有人命傷亡，財物損失都入大家數<br />\n<br />\n之後民意會逆轉，到時大家真係變成暴徒，場運動就會散<br />\n<br />\n以大局為重，今次又係和理非主場<br />\n<br />\n我地全日都會和平咁集會<br />\n<br />\n一旦遇到襲擊，希望勇武義士出手相助<br />\n<br />\n既然依家知道我方係唔會入村<br />\n<br />\n一旦有與我方衣著相似既人入村，可以安心假設佢地係中共派黎假扮既<br />\n<br />\n大家小心，香港加油"},{"pid":"44d412bc4fe02e755f50773f20f109479e18ea50","tid":1369733,"uid":222614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T18:44:48.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"12899c8e3bed1011dcf02d7b00ff0a962d1f7195","tid":1369733,"uid":272976,"like":59,"dislike":0,"score":59,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T18:44:51.000Z","msg":"依啲post夠未！？<br />\n一個月以嚟現場前線不嬲都智勇並重，唔好睇少班兄弟好唔好！？"},{"pid":"307dbc87671b6a763308b47ba10961abb779ddb8","tid":1369733,"uid":222614,"like":0,"dislike":29,"score":-29,"quote":{"pid":"12899c8e3bed1011dcf02d7b00ff0a962d1f7195","tid":1369733,"uid":272976,"like":59,"dislike":0,"score":59,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T18:44:51.000Z","msg":"依啲post夠未！？<br />\n一個月以嚟現場前線不嬲都智勇並重，唔好睇少班兄弟好唔好！？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T18:46:29.000Z","msg":"今次情況唔同，已肯定中共會派人假扮我方入村搞事"},{"pid":"94a3ec77dd643e96534e7be6d643e00682f66a33","tid":1369733,"uid":222614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T18:47:20.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"39f58a2452e473544a449748924cf0996ba82200","tid":1369733,"uid":1962,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T18:49:46.000Z","msg":"得架啦，大家知道係計啦<br />\n一勇武就又中計嘛，明啦明啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smi